  "macro_plan": "Niv to Light is a five-color midrange toolbox deck that leverages Bring to Light to access a wide array of silver bullets and threats tailored to the metagame. Its core engine revolves around Niv-Mizzet Reborn to generate massive card advantage and apply relentless pressure, supported by ramp like Sylvan Caryatid and a rebuilt mana base for consistency. The deck aims to stabilize early with efficient removal and board wipes, then snowball into a late-game state where chaining Nivs and using Kolaghan's Command for reach closes out games.",
